243
00:16:48,955 --> 00:16:51,105
Lično ću se pobrinuti za to.

244
00:16:51,275 --> 00:16:56,065
Uskoro ću biti s vama.

245
00:16:59,035 --> 00:16:59,785
Izgubili smo ih.

246
00:16:59,955 --> 00:17:01,385
Izgubili smo signal.

247
00:17:01,635 --> 00:17:02,515
Prokletstvo!

248
00:17:20,035 --> 00:17:22,915
Dame i gospodo,
počinjemo spuštanje na Fhloston.

249
00:17:23,355 --> 00:17:28,715
Sadu su 3.20.
Temperatura je 26 stepeni.

250
00:17:29,075 --> 00:17:31,275
Nadam se da ste uživali
u letu,

251
00:17:31,435 --> 00:17:33,395
i da ćete opet putovati s nama.

252
00:17:50,875 --> 00:17:53,755
Dame i gospodo,
dobrodošli u raj.

253
00:18:39,875 --> 00:18:41,545
Nametnici u glavnoj ventilaciji.

254
00:18:41,955 --> 00:18:43,545
Opet?
Ja ću to srediti.

255
00:18:52,275 --> 00:18:55,075
- Već smo stigli?
- Da.

256
00:18:55,555 --> 00:18:56,355
Dobro!

257
00:18:56,835 --> 00:19:00,385
Imamo 12 bazena i još
2 na krovu.

258
00:19:00,555 --> 00:19:03,355
svi restorani su duž
drugog i desetog kata.

259
00:19:03,515 --> 00:19:07,345
Planet Fhloston ima 400 plaža,
na kojima možete biti do 5.

260
00:19:07,515 --> 00:19:10,635
Zatim se brod diže
da bi uživali u ljepšem pogledu.

261
00:19:10,795 --> 00:19:12,065
Da li je Diva tu?

262
00:19:12,315 --> 00:19:13,355
Još ne.

263
00:19:13,675 --> 00:19:15,955
Ima li još karata
za operu?

264
00:19:16,115 --> 00:19:17,865
Imate rezervirano sedalo,
u prednjem redu.

265
00:19:18,115 --> 00:19:20,425
Pored Ruby Rhoda!

266
00:19:20,595 --> 00:19:23,105
Tako je talentiran. Volim ga.
Tako je seksi!

267
00:19:23,275 --> 00:19:26,475
On ima vašu ulaznicu.
Biće tu za 20 minuta.

268
00:19:28,195 --> 00:19:29,995
Gde mogu naći
nešto za obući?

269
00:19:33,315 --> 00:19:35,985
- Uživajte večeras gospodine Dallas.
- Hvala.

270
00:19:43,555 --> 00:19:46,435
Ti jadniče!
Nisam te trebala roditi

271
00:19:46,595 --> 00:19:50,035
Imala sam trudove danima,
i ovako mi vraćaš?

272
00:19:50,195 --> 00:19:51,385
Trebala sam nabaviti
robota.

273
00:19:51,555 --> 00:19:52,825
Ma daj, mama.

274
00:19:52,995 --> 00:19:55,355
Ja bih trebala biti tamo, a ne ti.
Ja želim potamnjeti.

275
00:19:55,515 --> 00:19:56,995
Trebam koktel.

276
00:20:18,915 --> 00:20:20,105
Unesite kovčeg.

277
00:20:24,035 --> 00:20:25,705
Dobrodošli, gospođo Diva.
Ja sam Fog.

278
00:20:25,835 --> 00:20:27,825
Dobrodošli na...
Ja sam...

279
00:20:28,195 --> 00:20:30,995
...iz osiguranja...
Dobrodošli na... !

280
00:20:49,995 --> 00:20:52,145
- Mogu li razgovarati s vama?
- Svakako!

281
00:20:56,235 --> 00:20:59,355
Gospođi Plava Laguna je drago
što ste tu.

282
00:20:59,515 --> 00:21:02,265
Dati će vam ono što tražite
posle koncerta.

283
00:21:02,435 --> 00:21:03,185
Ostanite ovde.

284
00:21:05,515 --> 00:21:09,505
Slušate Radio Cosmos.
Sada je 5 sati.

285
00:21:11,235 --> 00:21:12,275
kormilo na 1,08.

286
00:21:14,155 --> 00:21:15,475
kormilo 1,08!

287
00:21:15,755 --> 00:21:16,985
kormilo na 1,08.

288
00:21:18,235 --> 00:21:21,835
Vreme je da se pridružimo Ruby Rhodu
i Korben Dallasu,

289
00:21:21,995 --> 00:21:25,745
srećnom pobedniku
natecanja Gemini Croquette.

290
00:21:25,915 --> 00:21:28,955
Uživo,
sa Fhlostonskog...

291
00:21:29,235 --> 00:21:30,795
Raja!

292
00:21:30,955 --> 00:21:35,315
Ruby Rhod na raspolaganju sa Korbenom,
direktorom hotela,

293
00:21:35,595 --> 00:21:38,185
i Miss Gemini Croquette
u živo!

294
00:21:38,355 --> 00:21:40,395
I 8,000 ostalih srećnika,

295
00:21:40,555 --> 00:21:45,155
koji imaju čast uživati
u jedinstvenom koncertu gospođe Plava Laguna!

296
00:21:48,635 --> 00:21:50,595
Ulazimo u

297
00:21:50,835 --> 00:21:53,395
najlepšu koncertnu dvoranu
u celom svemiru!

298
00:21:53,555 --> 00:21:57,265
savršena kopija
stare operne kuće.

299
00:21:57,995 --> 00:21:59,315
Ali koga je briga za to?

300
00:22:00,435 --> 00:22:03,075
Na mojoj desnoj strani grupa,
ministara.

301
00:22:03,355 --> 00:22:06,635
Na mojoj levoj Baby Ray,
glumačka zvezda.

302
00:22:06,795 --> 00:22:09,515
Neće baš uživati u
ovom koncertu. Potpuno je gluv!

303
00:22:12,435 --> 00:22:16,395
Ovde je i Roy Von Baker,
kralj laser balla!

304
00:22:16,675 --> 00:22:19,105
Car kodar Japheta
i njegova ljupka kćerka.

305
00:22:19,275 --> 00:22:22,315
"Volim pevati",
poverila mi je nedavno.

306
00:22:22,475 --> 00:22:25,195
Imam snimku
njenog talentiranog glasa.

307
00:22:27,315 --> 00:22:29,115
Ostatak ću pustiti nakon koncerta.

308
00:22:29,275 --> 00:22:31,425
Vreme je da Korben nešto
kaže.

309
00:22:32,955 --> 00:22:37,025
Reci mi čoveče jesi li srećan
u ovom velikom svetu?

310
00:22:38,635 --> 00:22:39,675
Oduševljen.

311
00:22:41,555 --> 00:22:42,745
A sada...

312
00:22:43,155 --> 00:22:44,145
šampanjac!

313
00:22:50,115 --> 00:22:52,025
Reklame!
Reklame!

314
00:22:52,595 --> 00:22:54,025
Prekid od 30 sekundi.

315
00:23:09,835 --> 00:23:11,185
Snimamo.

316
00:24:59,035 --> 00:25:02,395
Brod u nevolji
traži dozvolu za sletanje.

317
00:25:02,555 --> 00:25:05,195
Stavi ga na sletište.
Obavesti osiguranje.

318
00:25:05,915 --> 00:25:08,555
- Imate dozvolu na jedan sat.
- Više nego što trebam.

319
00:25:23,155 --> 00:25:24,955
Šampanjac za Divu.

320
00:25:25,475 --> 00:25:26,545
Ja ću to uzeti.

321
00:25:59,835 --> 00:26:01,555
Našao sam!

322
00:26:34,915 --> 00:26:35,955
Uhvati je!

323
00:28:06,275 --> 00:28:07,625
Bila je zaseda.

324
00:28:11,275 --> 00:28:14,795
Ako žele rat,
imati će ga!

325
00:28:22,035 --> 00:28:23,755
Čestitke, mala damo.

326
00:28:23,915 --> 00:28:27,225
Hvala što ste obavili prljavi deo posla.
Ni sam ne bih izveo bolje.

327
00:28:28,555 --> 00:28:29,955
Predajte kamenje.

328
00:29:08,835 --> 00:29:10,825
Ne mičite se!
Preuzimamo brod!

329
00:29:15,355 --> 00:29:16,185
Ruke u vis.

330
00:30:22,075 --> 00:30:23,475
Prepoznajem ovu muziku.

331
00:30:26,075 --> 00:30:28,275
Promenimo ritam.

332
00:30:34,435 --> 00:30:36,265
Mislim da smo napadnuti.

333
00:30:36,515 --> 00:30:37,865
Posvuda su.

334
00:30:38,115 --> 00:30:40,705
Oni su ratnici i to ružni.

335
00:30:40,875 --> 00:30:44,185
Imaju velike zube, velike glave,
velike uši i smrde.

336
00:30:44,355 --> 00:30:45,155
Mangalori.

337
00:30:47,915 --> 00:30:50,115
Vlada me je poslala
da vam pomognem.

338
00:30:50,355 --> 00:30:52,235
Ako me neko čuje,
neka dođe po mene.

339
00:30:52,395 --> 00:30:54,145
Ja sam u prvom redu.

340
00:30:56,115 --> 00:30:57,785
Moraš joj dati kamenje.

341
00:30:57,955 --> 00:30:58,835
- Kome?

342
00:30:59,035 --> 00:31:00,545
Petom elementu.

343
00:31:00,675 --> 00:31:05,035
Vrhovnom biću koje je poslano na Zemlju
da spasi svemir.

344
00:31:05,195 --> 00:31:06,025
Leeloo?

345
00:31:08,435 --> 00:31:11,635
Ali ona je osetljivija
nego što izgleda.

346
00:31:12,155 --> 00:31:13,715
Treba tvoju pomoć...

347
00:31:14,835 --> 00:31:15,905
i tvoju ljubav,

348
00:31:16,755 --> 00:31:17,715
ili...

349
00:31:18,195 --> 00:31:20,025
će umreti.

350
00:31:24,355 --> 00:31:25,265
Ostanite sa mnom.

351
00:31:25,515 --> 00:31:26,635
U pomoć!

352
00:31:33,635 --> 00:31:37,105
Ako nešto želiš,
učini to sam.

353
00:31:38,395 --> 00:31:40,115
Hajde.
Ne možeš umreti.

354
00:31:40,435 --> 00:31:42,425
Probudi se!
Gde je kamenje?

355
00:31:42,675 --> 00:31:44,825
Gde je kamenje?

356
00:31:46,035 --> 00:31:47,075
Kamenje...

357
00:32:00,075 --> 00:32:01,585
Nije ovde.

358
00:32:02,915 --> 00:32:03,715
Gde je?

359
00:32:06,235 --> 00:32:07,875
U meni.

360
00:32:08,315 --> 00:32:09,305
Što?

361
00:32:16,155 --> 00:32:17,385
Bože moj! Korben!

362
00:32:17,635 --> 00:32:19,145
Još jedan dolazi.

363
00:32:19,355 --> 00:32:21,185
Mislim da se moramo maknuti odavde.

364
00:32:21,435 --> 00:32:22,345
Trenutak!

365
00:32:22,515 --> 00:32:23,505
Hej, ti!

366
00:32:24,955 --> 00:32:25,785
Da ti!

367
00:32:26,035 --> 00:32:27,625
- Ja nisam s njim.
- Gde su ostali?

368
00:32:30,435 --> 00:32:31,995
Rekao sam "trenutak".

369
00:32:32,155 --> 00:32:33,635
Ruby, drži oružje.

370
00:32:33,795 --> 00:32:35,275
Što želiš
da radim?

371
00:32:35,515 --> 00:32:36,315
Idemo.

372
00:32:36,475 --> 00:32:37,875
Stavi ruku na to.

373
00:32:38,035 --> 00:32:40,185
- Šta da radim?
- Ako se pomakne, pucaj.

374
00:32:41,555 --> 00:32:42,705
Ne osećam se dobro.

375
00:32:43,475 --> 00:32:45,985
Kamenje je u meni.

376
00:32:55,395 --> 00:32:57,595
Boli me glava
To nisam ja.

377
00:33:15,235 --> 00:33:16,355
Oprosti.

378
00:33:17,675 --> 00:33:18,745
Misliš da će biti u redu?

379
00:33:25,835 --> 00:33:28,225
Moj bože, Korben!
Još jedan dolazi!

380
00:33:30,835 --> 00:33:32,475
Sranje!
Trojica dolaze!

381
00:33:35,675 --> 00:33:38,105
Čuvaj ovo
svojim životom,

382
00:33:38,275 --> 00:33:40,505
ili ćeš izgledati kao on. Jasno?
- Jasno.

383
00:33:40,675 --> 00:33:41,475
Potpuno jasno?

384
00:33:41,875 --> 00:33:44,345
Ovako po vašem izgleda
diskretna operacija?

385
00:33:44,595 --> 00:33:48,305
Ne brinite se. Poznajem svog čoveka.
Smiriti će on situaciju.

386
00:34:14,595 --> 00:34:15,505
Pokret!

387
00:34:17,395 --> 00:34:18,305
Moj bože!

388
00:34:18,995 --> 00:34:21,715
Dame i gospodo,
ovo je zadivljujuće.

389
00:34:23,875 --> 00:34:25,145
Pusti mene.

390
00:34:32,275 --> 00:34:33,185
Moj bože!

391
00:34:33,355 --> 00:34:35,395
Korben Dallas,
je u nevolji.

392
00:34:38,635 --> 00:34:39,955
Hey! Ray!

393
00:34:42,115 --> 00:34:42,945
Oružje!

394
00:34:44,835 --> 00:34:46,475
Daj mi oružje!

395
00:34:46,715 --> 00:34:52,025
Probati ću se približiti
da bolje vidim.

396
00:35:08,035 --> 00:35:09,625
Da, oružje!

397
00:35:18,435 --> 00:35:19,505
Hvala, Ray.

398
00:35:20,595 --> 00:35:23,985
Ne pucajte! Ne pucajte!
Nisam naoružan!

399
00:35:24,155 --> 00:35:25,035
Ustani!

400
00:35:25,275 --> 00:35:27,635
Imate pogrešnog momka.
Ne pucajte.

401
00:35:27,835 --> 00:35:29,025
Nisam naoružan.

402
00:35:32,715 --> 00:35:33,515
Bože moj!

403
00:35:33,755 --> 00:35:37,195
Na odmoru sam.
Ne pucajte molim vas!

404
00:35:37,355 --> 00:35:38,315
Pobijedio sam na...

405
00:35:40,555 --> 00:35:41,515
natecanju,

406
00:35:41,675 --> 00:35:44,985
Gemini Croquette za...
Fhlostonski Raj.

407
00:35:47,355 --> 00:35:48,105
Dole.

408
00:35:50,635 --> 00:35:51,755
Samo trenutak...

409
00:35:51,955 --> 00:35:52,625
Dole!

410
00:35:54,595 --> 00:35:56,235
Pokušava nešto
reći.

411
00:35:56,435 --> 00:35:57,185
Dole!

412
00:36:11,115 --> 00:36:12,235
Oprosti!

413
00:36:21,475 --> 00:36:22,515
Gde si?

414
00:36:23,555 --> 00:36:26,195
Oh, moj... Oh, bože moj!
Korben!

415
00:36:26,435 --> 00:36:28,475
Dolaze!

416
00:36:32,635 --> 00:36:33,435
Ne miči se.

417
00:36:44,235 --> 00:36:45,275
Šta radiš?

418
00:36:45,515 --> 00:36:46,945
Broji do deset.

419
00:36:55,035 --> 00:36:57,235
- Je li to bila bomba?
-Ućuti i broji!

420
00:36:57,475 --> 00:36:59,595
1 , 2, 3, 4, 5...

421
00:36:59,875 --> 00:37:00,865
6...

422
00:37:01,075 --> 00:37:02,065
7, 8...

423
00:37:03,155 --> 00:37:04,505
9...

424
00:37:27,355 --> 00:37:28,265
...1 0.

425
00:37:34,555 --> 00:37:38,185
Vrlo sam razočaran!

426
00:37:38,755 --> 00:37:41,065
Što tražite?

427
00:37:41,235 --> 00:37:42,355
- Kontrolnu sobu.

428
00:37:44,195 --> 00:37:45,835
- To je.
- Ja ću biti tu.

429
00:37:46,355 --> 00:37:47,155
Idemo!

430
00:37:50,955 --> 00:37:52,275
Tišina!

431
00:37:53,435 --> 00:37:54,425
Ti si glavni?

432
00:37:55,835 --> 00:37:57,105
Koliko ih
je tamo vani?

433
00:37:58,275 --> 00:37:59,705
- Ne znam.
- Prebrojimo ih.

434
00:38:03,235 --> 00:38:05,035
Sedam levo,
pet desno.

435
00:38:11,355 --> 00:38:13,315
četiri desno,
i dva levo.

436
00:38:14,675 --> 00:38:17,145
Moramo pronaći vođu.
Neće se boriti bez njega.

437
00:38:17,435 --> 00:38:19,905
Još jedan pucanj,
i početi ćemo ubijati taoce.

438
00:38:20,955 --> 00:38:22,185
To je vođa.

439
00:38:22,355 --> 00:38:24,025
Pošaljite pregovarača.

440
00:38:26,195 --> 00:38:28,265
Još nikad nisam pregovarao.

441
00:38:28,635 --> 00:38:30,305
Mogu li ja... pokušati?

442
00:38:30,835 --> 00:38:32,265
Nemam, sigurno!

443
00:38:32,595 --> 00:38:35,065
Šaljemo vam
pregovarača.

444
00:38:43,435 --> 00:38:45,425
Želi li još
neko pregovarati?

445
00:38:45,595 --> 00:38:48,105
Gde je naučio
tako pregovarati?

446
00:38:48,715 --> 00:38:49,835
Pitam se!

447
00:38:54,515 --> 00:38:55,555
Gde je Ruby?

448
00:38:56,675 --> 00:38:57,865
Mislio sam da je mrtav.

449
00:38:58,075 --> 00:38:59,065
Gospodaru!

450
00:38:59,395 --> 00:39:02,225
Nije to bilo ništa.
Samo mala pomoć.

451
00:39:02,435 --> 00:39:06,115
Dame i gospodo,
ovde je Ruby Rhod, živ još uvek...

452
00:39:07,355 --> 00:39:09,185
Što nije u redu s tobom?
To boli!

453
00:39:15,595 --> 00:39:19,195
Mislim da si prilično ljut
na mene.

454
00:39:19,435 --> 00:39:22,155
Ali ja se borim za
plemeniti cilj.

455
00:39:22,315 --> 00:39:24,355
Pokušavaš spasiti svet.
Sećam se.

456
00:39:24,755 --> 00:39:26,955
U ovom trenutku,
pokušavam spasiti Leeloo.

457
00:39:27,195 --> 00:39:28,155
Ona je u nevolji?

458
00:39:28,355 --> 00:39:30,235
Kada Leeloo
nije u nevolji?

459
00:39:30,475 --> 00:39:32,275
-Gde je to?
- U divinom apartmanu.

460
00:39:36,115 --> 00:39:37,025
Leeloo!

461
00:39:37,435 --> 00:39:38,425
Drži se.

462
00:39:41,875 --> 00:39:44,915
Dođi. Kako si dospela
u takvu poziciju?

463
00:39:50,235 --> 00:39:53,225
Tu sam. Sve je u redu.
Sve je Ok, sada.

464
00:39:57,235 --> 00:39:59,955
Imam kamenje.
Polako, u redu?

465
00:40:02,755 --> 00:40:06,195
Čoveče, što je ova stvar
sa svim tim brojevima?

466
00:40:14,235 --> 00:40:17,465
Ne, ne, ne.
Da je ovo bomba,

467
00:40:17,635 --> 00:40:21,385
uključio bi se alarm.
Svi hoteli imaju detektore za bombe.

468
00:40:23,795 --> 00:40:25,995
Ovo je uzbuna tipa A.

469
00:40:26,875 --> 00:40:30,705
Zbog sigurnosnih razloga,
Hotel mora biti evakuiran.

470
00:40:30,875 --> 00:40:33,515
Nastavite mirno
prema čamcima za spasavanje

471
00:40:33,835 --> 00:40:35,235
koji su smešteni u glavnoj dvorani.

472
00:40:35,435 --> 00:40:36,555
Ostanite mirni!

473
00:40:42,155 --> 00:40:44,435
Znaš kako se ovo zaustavlja,
Zar ne?

474
00:40:50,235 --> 00:40:53,465
Dva minuta
do završetka evakuiranja.

475
00:40:55,395 --> 00:40:56,275
Natrag!

476
00:40:56,435 --> 00:40:57,755
Evakuacija!

477
00:40:57,995 --> 00:41:01,145
Žao mi je, ne možete ostati ovde.
U hotelu je bomba.

478
00:41:05,555 --> 00:41:06,955
Znam.

479
00:41:21,155 --> 00:41:22,745
Ne želim umreti!

480
00:41:23,995 --> 00:41:25,425
Ulazi!

481
00:41:30,715 --> 00:41:33,755
Minut do potpune evakuacije.

482
00:41:37,795 --> 00:41:38,705
Ova.

483
00:41:42,155 --> 00:41:43,905
45 sekundi.

484
00:41:46,635 --> 00:41:48,195
Priveži je.

485
00:41:53,915 --> 00:41:55,875
Znaš li upravljati ovim?

486
00:41:56,035 --> 00:41:57,265
To je kao da voziš taksi.

487
00:42:01,835 --> 00:42:03,475
Kako ćemo
izaći kroz vrata?

488
00:42:16,715 --> 00:42:18,545
15 sekundi.

489
00:42:22,715 --> 00:42:25,515
10... 9... 8...

490
00:42:26,795 --> 00:42:27,755
7...

491
00:42:28,195 --> 00:42:29,235
6...

492
00:42:29,715 --> 00:42:30,705
5...

493
00:42:46,875 --> 00:42:48,765
Za čast...

494
00:42:52,795 --> 00:42:53,625
O ne!

495
00:42:54,395 --> 00:42:55,225
Drži se.

496
00:43:16,555 --> 00:43:17,985
Kao da voziš taksi...

497
00:43:20,035 --> 00:43:22,625
7 je sati.
Vreme za vesti.

498
00:43:22,795 --> 00:43:25,025
Vidimo se sutra
u novoj pustolovini.

499
00:43:25,195 --> 00:43:26,385
Kraj emitiranja.

500
00:43:27,075 --> 00:43:29,115
To je nejbolja emisija
koju sam ikada snimio.

501
00:43:31,955 --> 00:43:34,595
Major Dallas ima
ukrcano svih 5 elemenata.

502
00:43:34,835 --> 00:43:37,715
Sveštenik ih vodi
prema hramu.

503
00:43:41,675 --> 00:43:43,235
Spašeni smo!

504
00:43:58,955 --> 00:44:01,105
Diva je rekla
da se moram brinuti o tebi.

505
00:44:02,235 --> 00:44:04,705
Ljudski postupci su tako čudni.

506
00:44:04,875 --> 00:44:06,275
Kako to misliš?

507
00:44:07,755 --> 00:44:11,275
Sve što stvorite
upotrebljava se za uništavanje.

508
00:44:11,835 --> 00:44:14,905
Da...
Mi to zovemo ljudskom prirodom.

509
00:44:15,195 --> 00:44:16,915
To si naučila
sa televizije.

510
00:44:17,075 --> 00:44:20,275
Još nisam završila.
Stigla sam do slova V.

511
00:44:20,515 --> 00:44:23,505
"V" je dobro...
neke dobre reči počinju slovom "V".

512
00:44:24,075 --> 00:44:25,475
Kao?

513
00:44:27,755 --> 00:44:28,985
Valiant...

514
00:44:29,715 --> 00:44:30,755
Vrijedan...

515
00:44:33,075 --> 00:44:34,795
Vrlo lepo.

516
00:44:46,435 --> 00:44:48,155
Naravno, Munro!

517
00:44:49,515 --> 00:44:50,705
Gospodine predsedniče?

518
00:44:50,995 --> 00:44:52,065
Šta je sad?

519
00:44:54,915 --> 00:44:56,585
Imamo problem.

520
00:45:02,115 --> 00:45:03,235
Približava se?

521
00:45:03,595 --> 00:45:06,955
Ne samo da se približava.
Kreće se neverovatnom brzinom.

522
00:45:11,075 --> 00:45:14,275
Imate li neku ideju
kuda ide?

523
00:45:20,835 --> 00:45:23,715
To je general
na... telefonu.

524
00:45:24,475 --> 00:45:25,955
Spojit ću vas
s predsednikom.

525
00:45:27,395 --> 00:45:30,035
Pozdravljam vas kao
ratnika.

526
00:45:30,275 --> 00:45:32,785
Sjajan ste primer
ove vojske. ..

527
00:45:32,955 --> 00:45:34,145
Gospodine predsedniče,

528
00:45:34,315 --> 00:45:36,435
kada ćete konačno
preći na stvar?

529
00:45:39,755 --> 00:45:43,275
Vatrena kugla promera 1,200 milja
leti pravo u smeru Zemlje.

530
00:45:43,515 --> 00:45:46,795
Ne zanmo kako bi je zaustavili.
U tome je stvar.

531
00:45:49,475 --> 00:45:51,355
Koliko vremana
imamo?

532
00:45:53,075 --> 00:45:55,635
Ako brzina ostane nepromijenjena,
1 sat i 57 minuta.

533
00:45:56,035 --> 00:45:58,265
Nazvati ću vas
za dva sata.

534
00:45:59,435 --> 00:46:00,555
Halo?

535
00:47:08,595 --> 00:47:10,425
Upravo su se  spustili
u pustinji.

536
00:47:12,875 --> 00:47:14,065
Dobaro obavljeno, David!

537
00:47:16,035 --> 00:47:18,105
- Stavite je u sredinu.
- Gde? Tu?

538
00:47:25,355 --> 00:47:29,235
- Otkrili ste što je?
-Ovo bi trebala biti vatra.

539
00:47:30,115 --> 00:47:32,505
- Znate li kako ovo radi?
- Teorijski.

540
00:47:32,675 --> 00:47:35,475
Četiri kamena se
moraju postaviti uokolo.

541
00:47:35,635 --> 00:47:37,385
Peti element bi trebao biti
u sredini,

542
00:47:37,555 --> 00:47:39,985
i tada bi oružje protiv Zla
moralo raditi.

543
00:47:40,755 --> 00:47:43,825
- Nikad niste videli kako radi?
- Ne.

544
00:47:44,355 --> 00:47:47,425
Svako oružje ima upustvo.
Mora postojati i za ovo.

545
00:47:55,955 --> 00:47:58,595
Tako je!
Spojite simbole, idemo!

546
00:48:00,035 --> 00:48:00,865
Vetar...

547
00:48:02,715 --> 00:48:04,385
Šta radiš?

548
00:48:04,675 --> 00:48:06,425
- Što?
- Šta radiš?

549
00:48:07,635 --> 00:48:09,545
Pokušava te
održati u tvom poslu.

550
00:48:13,195 --> 00:48:14,075
Vatra...

551
00:48:15,675 --> 00:48:16,505
Gotovo!

552
00:48:16,675 --> 00:48:18,075
Šta sada?

553
00:48:18,235 --> 00:48:20,145
Sada,
ih moramo otvoriti.

554
00:48:21,315 --> 00:48:23,625
Znate kako to možete učiniti,
zar ne?

555
00:48:23,795 --> 00:48:25,225
Teorijski...

556
00:48:26,435 --> 00:48:27,475
Ne.

557
00:48:31,915 --> 00:48:33,315
Leeloo, probudi se!

558
00:48:33,835 --> 00:48:37,145
Moraš nam pomoći.
Kako se kamenje otvara?

559
00:48:38,995 --> 00:48:40,585
Vetar puše...

560
00:48:42,355 --> 00:48:43,585
Vatra gori...

561
00:48:43,795 --> 00:48:46,915
Sve to znam
Ali, kako se otvara kamenje?

562
00:48:47,435 --> 00:48:48,705
Kiša...

563
00:48:51,715 --> 00:48:52,785
...pada.

564
00:48:57,035 --> 00:48:58,025
Leeloo!

565
00:48:59,435 --> 00:49:00,665
Što to znači?

566
00:49:02,235 --> 00:49:03,635
Mislim...

567
00:49:03,835 --> 00:49:06,305
Možda je to zagonetka,
igra ili tako nešto.

568
00:49:06,795 --> 00:49:09,305
Ako ne otvorimo ovo kamenje za 5 minuta,
mrtvi smo.

569
00:49:10,115 --> 00:49:11,075
Da, mrtvi!

570
00:49:23,155 --> 00:49:24,385
Prekasno.

571
00:49:25,955 --> 00:49:27,625
Izgubili smo vezu s njim.

572
00:49:27,995 --> 00:49:29,225
3 minuta.

573
00:49:30,115 --> 00:49:33,475
Mislim da je moj slomljen.
Zašto sam morao dobiti slomljenog?

574
00:49:41,715 --> 00:49:43,545
Nikad nam neće uspeti.

575
00:49:48,035 --> 00:49:49,945
Korben! Miče se!

576
00:49:52,195 --> 00:49:54,235
- Pokaži mi što si napravio.
- Ništa.

577
00:49:54,395 --> 00:49:55,905
Ućuti!

578
00:49:56,075 --> 00:49:59,385
Smiri se i pokaži mi što si učinio,
korak po korak.

579
00:49:59,555 --> 00:50:03,385
Stajao sam tu.
stavio sam ruke na vrh,

580
00:50:03,555 --> 00:50:05,195
i rekao...

581
00:50:05,915 --> 00:50:07,745
Nikad nećemo uspeti.

582
00:50:09,515 --> 00:50:10,395
Samo to?

583
00:50:19,275 --> 00:50:20,075
Korben...

584
00:50:20,955 --> 00:50:21,835
Vetar...

585
00:50:22,875 --> 00:50:25,155
Rekla je da vetar puše.

586
00:50:32,595 --> 00:50:33,945
Svi uzmite kamen.

587
00:50:34,195 --> 00:50:36,945
Voda za vodu, vatra za vatru,
zemlja za zemlju. Idemo!

588
00:50:39,595 --> 00:50:40,345
Zemlja...

589
00:50:40,915 --> 00:50:42,185
Još jedan je otvoren.

590
00:50:57,595 --> 00:50:59,825
Korben, čoveče!
Nemam vatru.

591
00:50:59,915 --> 00:51:01,955
Nemam šibice.
Imaš ti koju?

592
00:51:02,195 --> 00:51:04,395
Prestao sam pušiti.
Ti pušiš?

593
00:51:04,675 --> 00:51:07,665
Ima li neko šibice?
Treba nam vatra.

594
00:51:17,235 --> 00:51:18,425
Ne dišite.

595
00:51:37,075 --> 00:51:38,065
Vatra.

596
00:51:38,795 --> 00:51:39,675
Jedan minut.

597
00:51:40,315 --> 00:51:41,635
Idemo, Leeloo!

598
00:51:41,795 --> 00:51:44,185
Probudi se.
Moraš obaviti svoj deo posla.

599
00:51:45,355 --> 00:51:46,545
Zaštiti život...

600
00:51:47,835 --> 00:51:48,905
od smrti.

601
00:51:49,075 --> 00:51:50,195
Slušaj me!

602
00:51:50,835 --> 00:51:51,955
Slušaj!

603
00:51:52,275 --> 00:51:54,705
Znam da si umorna.

604
00:51:54,875 --> 00:51:58,785
Odvesti ću te na odmor.
Pravi odmor samo ti i ja.

605
00:51:58,955 --> 00:52:01,385
Ali ako sada ne učiniš nešto
svi ćemo umreti.

606
00:52:01,555 --> 00:52:05,435
Kakvog ima smisla spašavati život
kada vidiš što radite s njim?

607
00:52:05,955 --> 00:52:08,155
Ući će u atmosferu
za 40 sekundi.

608
00:52:09,755 --> 00:52:11,185
U pravu si,

609
00:52:11,395 --> 00:52:15,945
ali postoje neke lepe stvari
koje vredi spasiti.

610
00:52:16,075 --> 00:52:17,795
Prekrasne stvari!

611
00:52:19,035 --> 00:52:20,355
Kao ljubav?

612
00:52:20,675 --> 00:52:24,905
Da, to je dobar primer.
Ljubav vredi spasiti.

613
00:52:25,875 --> 00:52:27,465
Ne znam što je ljubav.

614
00:52:29,515 --> 00:52:30,785
Ne zanm što je ljubav.

615
00:52:30,995 --> 00:52:33,195
Stvorena sam da štitim,
ne da volim.

616
00:52:33,435 --> 00:52:36,075
Za mene ne postoji ništa drugo
osim toga.

617
00:52:36,275 --> 00:52:37,945
Grešiš!

618
00:52:39,355 --> 00:52:40,475
Ja te trebam.

619
00:52:40,555 --> 00:52:42,065
Jako te trebam.

620
00:52:43,955 --> 00:52:44,995
Zašto?

621
00:52:47,075 --> 00:52:48,145
Zato...

622
00:52:48,515 --> 00:52:49,705
zato...

623
00:52:50,635 --> 00:52:52,435
Reci joj, Korben.

624
00:52:54,595 --> 00:52:56,795
Reci mi molim te.

625
00:52:57,035 --> 00:52:58,915
Trebaš li me?

626
00:52:59,555 --> 00:53:00,705
Zato...

627
00:53:00,995 --> 00:53:02,145
Reci mi.

628
00:53:06,035 --> 00:53:07,515
Zato što te volim.

629
00:53:08,715 --> 00:53:09,785
Volim te.

630
00:53:13,675 --> 00:53:15,425
Deset, devet...

631
00:53:15,595 --> 00:53:16,475
osam...

632
00:53:16,675 --> 00:53:17,945
sedam, šest...

633
00:53:18,675 --> 00:53:19,665
pet...

634
00:53:20,115 --> 00:53:21,435
četiri, tri...

635
00:53:21,755 --> 00:53:22,795
dva...

636
00:53:23,195 --> 00:53:24,105
jedan...

637
00:54:00,355 --> 00:54:04,635
Skeneri potvrđuju da je
tamni planet mrtav.

638
00:54:04,875 --> 00:54:07,865
Čini se da se zaustavio
62 milje pre udara..

639
00:54:20,435 --> 00:54:22,395
Što nije u redu?
Zašto vičeš?

640
00:54:22,555 --> 00:54:24,785
Svakih 5 minuta
je tu omba ili nešto slično!

641
00:54:24,955 --> 00:54:26,145
Odlazim.

642
00:54:40,435 --> 00:54:41,555
Gospodine predsedniče...

643
00:54:41,715 --> 00:54:44,355
Dozvolite da vas upoznam
sa profesorom Mactilburgh.

644
00:54:44,555 --> 00:54:46,225
Čast mi je gospodine predsedniče.

645
00:54:46,395 --> 00:54:47,585
Gde su moji junaci?

646
00:54:47,755 --> 00:54:51,745
Umorni su od svojih zadataka,
pa smo ih stavili u reaktor.

647
00:54:52,035 --> 00:54:53,755
Imam još 19 sastanaka nakon ovog.

648
00:54:53,955 --> 00:54:56,155
Pogledaću da li
su se oporavili.

649
00:54:56,595 --> 00:54:57,475
Hvala.

650
00:54:57,635 --> 00:54:59,705
Idemo uživo za jedan minut.

651
00:55:07,955 --> 00:55:09,225
Oni...

652
00:55:10,595 --> 00:55:11,665
nisu spremni.

653
00:55:12,635 --> 00:55:14,835
Treba im još...
5 minuta.

654
00:55:15,075 --> 00:55:16,955
Imate 20 sekundi.

655
00:55:17,115 --> 00:55:18,865
Ne, gospođo.
Ne, pokušavam.

656
00:55:19,035 --> 00:55:19,945
Ko je to?

657
00:55:20,115 --> 00:55:21,755
Kaže da je
Korbenova majka.

658
00:55:21,915 --> 00:55:22,955
Dajte mi je.

659
00:55:24,035 --> 00:55:26,625
Gospođo Dallas,
ovde Predsednik.

660
00:55:26,795 --> 00:55:29,265
U ime Federacije...

661
00:55:29,435 --> 00:55:31,425
Čak i ne zvučiš
kao on!

662
00:55:31,595 --> 00:55:34,105
Predsednik je idiot.
Ti ne zvučiš tako.

663
00:55:34,275 --> 00:55:36,835
Ako ne želiš razgovarati sa svojom majkom
samo me izbegavaj kao i obično.

664
00:55:36,995 --> 00:55:39,585
Bacit ću se pod auto.
Leći ću u krevet...

